  "description": "Breach threshold set so low that the compressor fires on almost every cycle of LFO1. Each breach event drives the sub layer into the mix, creating an irregular thud underneath the fast wavetable scan. The pod is breaching chaotically — sonar on, body airborne, then back into the depth. Unstable surface tension.",
